{"tid":2415793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安心出行開發商｜創奇思獲中資撐腰私隱恐送中 曾搞香港小姐投票冧檔","createTime":"2021-02-20T13:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T13:55:12.000Z","uid":72533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"24ad2f6a7a446e8f4fecd2e51c2be36f520cf469","tid":2415793,"uid":72533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:55:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/us/20201214/GY5PDQQYGNHGLKP3DMJ72JIAFE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fus%2F20201214%2FGY5PDQQYGNHGLKP3DMJ72JIAFE%2F&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2Bbksv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=a0950875\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fus%2F20201214%2FGY5PDQQYGNHGLKP3DMJ72JIAFE%2F&h=236b0bb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/us/20201214/GY5PDQQYGNHGLKP3DMJ72JIAFE/</a><br />\n不過本刊發現「安心出行」問題多多，應用程式有漏洞，私隱安全無保障，而開發商創奇思（Cherrypicks）在過去曾為大台香港小姐搞「全民公投」，伺服器卻「打柴」令大熱門女神朱千雪失落港姐冠軍寶座，擁有經典黑歷史的它，依然獲得這個全港性大Project，或因其背景親中。由香港人趙子翹開設的本土公司創奇思，數年前漸靠近大陸，幕後「金主」是網龍（777）。"}]}